rs/jancborchardt/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-08-01t12:49:01z","updated_at":"2013-08-01t12:49:01z","body":"itâ€™s default on, but this issue is about if we can completely remove it. iâ€™d still ponder it."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/26122205","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3918#issuecomment-26122205","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3918","id":26122205,"user":{"login":"weberhofer","id":793251,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/b521dd9262d61f3b198ccf8905cf2a27?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f5ecd50bf46024ab27630a04981f20216.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"b521dd9262d61f3b198ccf8905cf2a27","url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer","html_url":"https://github.com/weberhofer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-10-11t08:36:03z","updated_at":"2013-10-11t08:36:03z","body":"removing that checkbox and checking it as standard value is a very bad idea from the security perspective, because users who work on shared computers can easily forget to log-off now, as they have to do that explicitly.\r\n\r\nfor users who want to stay logged-in, there is not much overhead to enable the function, as will not see the complete login-form again - they are automatically logged in!\r\n\r\ni vote for setting the old default or at least allowing the admin-user to set the default value or even to disable the stay-logged-in functionality completely; that would be a great thing for professional users."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/26122417","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3918#issuecomment-26122417","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3918","id":26122417,"user":{"login":"jancborchardt","id":925062,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f84ec51f9ceed468217d4e13abf78da9c.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"2fd3f4d5d762955e5b603794a888fa97","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt","html_url":"https://github.com/jancborchardt","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jancborchardt/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-10-11t08:39:52z","updated_at":"2013-10-11t08:39:52z","body":"iâ€™ll close this issue because iâ€™m convinced by the arguments that fully removing the checkbox is probably a security issue.\r\n\r\nbut we will not reinstate the old default of needing to explicitly check that you want to stay logged in. nor introduce yet another admin setting â€¦ come on, we design software so that life is easier for users and admins, not that they need to fiddle around and choose settings all the time."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/26127205","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3918#issuecomment-26127205","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3918","id":26127205,"user":{"login":"weberhofer","id":793251,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/b521dd9262d61f3b198ccf8905cf2a27?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f5ecd50bf46024ab27630a04981f20216.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"b521dd9262d61f3b198ccf8905cf2a27","url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer","html_url":"https://github.com/weberhofer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/weberhofer/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-10-11t10:15:55z","updated_at":"2013-10-11t10:15:55z","body":"yes, another setting is possibly to much. but select this per default is imho a security issue."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/27366293","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3918#issuecomment-27366293","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3918","id":27366293,"user":{"login":"john7000","id":4946224,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/1031842c3b604f90657fe72f029fd1cf?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f2bcf57f0a0aefb05cb0d70b0d73def1f.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"1031842c3b604f90657fe72f029fd1cf","url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000","html_url":"https://github.com/john7000","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/john7000/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-10-30t05:33:30z","updated_at":"2013-10-30t05:33:30z","body":"i don't like this default either expecially for a software product which claims \"web services under your control\". i'd prefer a user to be explicitly responsible for leaving their credentials cached on someone elses browser and have to explain why the private or confidential data they were entrusted with has become public rather than have the user need to explicitly remember to disable the option every time they use oc via the browser on a work peer or friend's machine. its not much effort to tick the box just once on browsers in 1-2 single-user os accounts but recovering from a serious data leak or identity theft can cost a fortune and be extremely painful.\r\ni tried the following which seems to work\r\nedit the owncloud file at \r\nowncloud/core/templates/login.php\r\ngo to line 39 (oc 5.0.12) and remove the word \"checked\" (column 78) from the attribute list for the checkbox.  \r\n              ... input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"remember_login\" value=\"1\" id=\"remember_login\" checked ...\r\nbecomes \r\n              ... input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"remember_login\" value=\"1\" id=\"remember_login\" ... \r\n   \r\n"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/30248669","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/3918#issuecomment-30248669","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/3918","id":30248669,"user":{"login":"bastei","id":5174055,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/20c8660df852ebc09ecdae4d1394cab5?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f5cbed2271876d6c004d9fc55e968359f.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"20c8660df852ebc09ecdae4d1394cab5","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei","html_url":"https://github.com/bastei","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bastei/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-12-10t17:27:35z","updated_at":"2013-12-10t17:27:35z","body":"to check the remember-box by default is really a bad usability fault! every time i login i wonder why the decision for this cumbersome behavior was made.\r\n\r\ni don't know any website where this is checked by default and this is not only the expected behavior but also with good cause: people who don't want to be remembered have to tick the box <b>every time</b> they login. the other way round people who want to stay logged in would <b>only need one</b> click when they are visiting the site first.\r\n\r\n\r\n> come on, we design software so that life 